          "id": "insight-text",
          "component": "Text",
          "variant": "body",
          "text": { "literalString": "Insight: Focus has a critical win rate problem at 10.7% — nearly 9 in 10 opportunities are lost. Despite carrying the second-largest won value ($43.2M), 4,625 opportunities were lost worth $262.6M. Key Core at 23.8% is also below par. Special Team's 94.9% is exceptional but operates at a much smaller scale ($10.9M won value)." }
        },
        {
          "id": "recommendation-card",
          "component": "Card",
          "children": ["recommendation-text"]
        },
        {
          "id": "recommendation-text",
          "component": "Text",
          "variant": "body",
          "text": { "literalString": "Recommendation: Prioritize a win/loss deep-dive on Focus — review qualification criteria, competitive positioning, and pricing. The low win rate combined with its large budget makes it the highest-leverage improvement opportunity across all categories." }
        },
        {
          "id": "citation-text",
          "component": "Text",
          "variant": "caption",
          "text": { "literalString": "Source: Q1 2026 US Select Whitepaper, p. 5 (60.5% aggregate win rate) · AskEPM illustrative drill-down by product category" }
        }
